Um... Excuse me. I apologize for interrupting while things are
getting exciting... But there's something I need to tell you
here...

\SE[12]... Can you leave us alone for a bit? Don't you understand
that it was a good atmosphere? \SE[13] Could you please be
considerate and read the mood a little...?

Eh, ah, sorry... I also feel bad about it. But, you see... this
is a trial version, you know.

For now, let's call it quits here... I think you've got a sense
of what kind of game it is, right...

\SE[12]... What are you talking about? Our yuri scene isn't
included. \SE[13] It's just filled with other people's ecchi
scenes.

\SE[12]And besides, there aren't enough of my cool scenes either.
I have to show Laura that I can be reliable. \SE[13]...I wonder
if I can't just be satisfied on my own.

Well, I understand how you feel... But you kind of got the
atmosphere and the feel of the battles, right? I think that's
what a trial version is supposed to be...
↓ピクチャを右から左に３割りほどスライドする

\SE\SE[0]I didn't ask for such boring circumstances. \.What's
important is our lovey-dovey moments, right? \!\SE[0]It would be
a waste of time to end without seeing that.

Ahh!! That's something for later!! Hurry, put it away!! Put it
away!!
SEに合わせるくらいの不満そうな速度で。
ウェイトはあってもいいかも

...So, for the continuation, we would like you to purchase it on
various sales sites....

W-Well...? We're not running a charity here, you know... That's
why there's a trial version for that...

\SE[33]S-Stop...! \!\SE[92]I think there's no helping it with
this...! \.I believe the person who made it also has a life and
all...

\SE[84]And besides, you know... There are times when paying money
makes things more enjoyable. \SE[21]I think it's important to
cherish that time... and believe in it.

\SE[52]I'm not completely convinced, but... if Laura says so,
I'll endure it...\SE[53]
\SE[22]\SM[rock]You did well enduring it. Good girl...

Well, that's how it is. The data from the trial version can be
transferred to the full version, so please check the included
manual when that time comes.

Ah, in the trial version you can't proceed any further. We would
like you to purchase the full version...

Ah, are you okay with the transfer method? I don't think I need
to explain it to someone who knows the details...!

I think when you started the demo version, there were a lot of
folders. There should be a folder called save in there.

Take that to the same place in the full version. With this, you
should be able to continue playing. Make sure to always make a
backup.
